{"id":173856,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011823/","date":"2011-08-24T02:00:23Z","modified":"2011-08-24T02:00:23Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/23","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约书评》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nybooks.com/blogs/nyrblog/2011/aug/22/chinas-liberation-tibet-rules-game/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国‘解放’西藏</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——从习近平在拉萨纪念仪式上的讲话看中国未来领导人的政策</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110823/ap_on_re_as/as_china_tibet\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国班禅喇嘛结束了拉卜楞寺之行</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，他称对当地的宗教自由印象深刻。但这样的评论可能会加深当地藏人的感觉，他不是真正的班禅喇嘛</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/23/chinese-artist-creates-corruption-hall-of-fame/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国画家建立“贪官名人堂”</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国画家张秉坚创立</span></span><span><span>“</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">贪官名人堂</span></span><span><span>”</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，让贪官入画。他说，</span></span><span><span>&#8220;</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">这一创意，是想推动人民思考，为什么在中国发生腐败？为什么中国的贪官这么多？怎样制止腐败</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/08/23/challenges-to-chinas-civil-society/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国民间社团所面临的挑战</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——近期“慈善机构”爆出的丑闻，也显示出非政府组织在中国面临的一些困难</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-opposition-presidential-candidate-seeks-peace-and-trade-with-china/2011/08/23/gIQA51F0XJ_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">民进党总统候选人蔡英文说，她当选后将努力维护两岸和平</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，继续与中共邻居保持大规模商贸关</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">系</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/23/senior-china-rail-exec-dies-as-high-speed-crash-probe-proceeds/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国铁路系统高管在事故调查中死亡</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/24/business/global/surveys-show-growth-in-europe-is-nearly-at-standstill.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">问卷调查显示中国和德国的发展速度将有所降低</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——但离衰退或硬着陆还远</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基国际和平基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45390&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的经济增长与美国的挑战与机会</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——经济学家黄育空接受</span>c-span<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">采访，称中国会继续保持两位数经济增长。</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：中国政府官员说，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.sacbee.com/2011/08/22/3854739/china-says-libyan-oil-projects.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在利比亚的油气项目对两国都很重要，希望局势尽快稳定</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。北京说，它乐于与反政府军合作重建，尊重利比亚人民的选择</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国崛起博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.mcclatchydc.com/china/2011/08/china-libya-and-the-cost-of-doing-business.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国、利比亚和经商成本</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国人在国外做生意一向以不干预当地政治著称。但在利比亚，当地人民对中国的做法却不甚满意</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2089934,00.html?xid=rss-world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+time/world+%28TIME:+Top+World+Stories%29&#038;utm_content=Google+Reader\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡扎菲就要倒下，阿萨德会是一下个吗</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/22/libya.gadhafi.mustapha.ben.halim/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">利比亚前总理说，卡扎菲不会不战而</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">降</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《悉尼晨报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.smh.com.au/business/world-business/strausskahn-sex-charges-dropped-20110823-1j78c.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国检察官请求法官，放弃对前</span>IMF<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">总裁卡恩的全部指控</span></a></span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>IDC: <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.idc.com/getdoc.jsp?containerId=prUS22997711\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国超过美国，成为世界最大</span>PC<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">市场</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——二季度销售数据显示中国完成了这一超越</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/kenrapoza/2011/08/22/is-china-bad-for-the-us-job-market/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国毁了美国的就业市场？</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——答案一言难尽</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/23/heaven-no-place-on-earth-for-china-developers/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国房地产商风光不再</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——今年以来，房地产销售量持续下降，房地产商的日子不太好过</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/multinationals-rush-to-court-chinas-consumers/2011/08/03/gIQA5W97WJ_gallery.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">跨国公司讨好中国消费者</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><b><span> </span></b></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>Penn-Olson<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.penn-olson.com/2011/08/23/china-intranet/?utm_source=twitterfeed&#038;utm_medium=twitter&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+PennOlson+%28Penn+Olson%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的网页浏览量</span>96%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">局限于国内网站</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——跟北朝鲜只差</span>4<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个百分点</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">单位：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.danwei.com/peoples-pornography-an-interview-with-katrien-jacobs/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">专访《大众色情——中国互联网上的色情与监控》一书作者</span><span>Katrien Jacobs</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">博士</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21526300?fsrc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">世界之家——香港重庆大厦众生相</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/23/lady-gaga-katy-perry-china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国下令网站撤掉一百首外国流行歌曲</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——因为这些歌曲的内容没有经过报批审查</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">迷途老外博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.lostlaowai.com/blog/china-stuff/from-peking-to-beijing-a-long-and-bumpy-trip/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从</span>Peking<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">到</span>Beijing</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——汉语拼音在西方世界的推广</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2011/aug/23/china-women-supreme-court-bride-price\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国女士力争半边天</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——尽管在中国最高领导层鲜见女性，但在日常生活中，中国妇女的地位的确不容小看</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-5160355866950953183?l=yyyyiiii